Package core

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Entity
    The interface of an entity object of the game engine, every object to be handled and rendered should implement this interface
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Camera
    The class that handles the camera of the game engine
    Engine
    This class is the main Engine class and handles all aspects of the EosGameEngine.
    Item
    This class handles each individual element in the engine
    Renderer
    This class handles the rendering of all items in the game engine
    Window
    This class implements the window where the game engine instance should be run
